data.value: Super Meat Boy and all related assets are property of Team Meat. SMB Launcher is a completely free fan-created program. This program does not violate the integrity of the game. This program simply provides extra features to it's users that are not available directly through the game but are however possible outside of it. This program automates these manual options. No affiliation with Team Meat or Speedrun.com
